flowchart TD
  A[(Old resumes, LinkedIn exports, notes, pasted text)] --> M[(Master OCF)]
  B[LLM-assisted import] --> M
  C[OCF editor app] --> M
  D[Hand editing] --> M

  M --> K[Curator / Deriver]
  J[Target context: job description, audience, purpose] -. guides .-> K

  K --> O[(Derived OCF)]

  O --> R[Renderer]
  R --> P[(Resume, cover letter, profile, PDF, HTML)]

  O --> E[Exporter]
  E --> X[(JSON Resume, LER-RS, Schema.org, LinkedIn paste, ATS import)]

  O --> C2[Coach or reviewer]
  C2 --> Q{Questions, corrections, new stories}

  P --> U{User Review}
  X --> U
  C2 --> U

  U --> F[(Output Files)]
  U --> Q

  Q --> V{Accepted updates only}
  V --> M
